/Users/zaihuilou/.local/lib/node_modules/openclaw/CHANGELOG.md:69:- Signal/config validation: add `channels.signal.groups` schema support so per-group `requireMention`, `tools`, and `toolsBySender` overrides no longer get rejected during config validation. (#27199) Thanks @unisone.
/Users/zaihuilou/.local/lib/node_modules/openclaw/CHANGELOG.md:243:- Telegram/docs: clarify that `channels.telegram.groups` allowlists chats while `groupAllowFrom` allowlists users inside those chats, and point invalid negative chat IDs at the right config key. (#42451) Thanks @altaywtf.
